Package: wellbeing-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dbus
Description: Digital Wellbeing common files
 D-Bus system policy files and systemd units shared across all
 Digital Wellbeing components.

Package: wellbeing-daemon
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, wellbeing-common, dbus
Description: Digital Wellbeing system daemon
 Root-owned system service that tracks app usage, enforces policies,
 and exposes the org.wellbeing.v1.Controller D-Bus API.

Package: wellbeing-gui
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, wellbeing-common, dbus
Description: Digital Wellbeing desktop GUI
 gpui desktop client for viewing usage reports and managing policies.
 Connects to the daemon exclusively over D-Bus; does not access
 SQLite directly.

Package: wellbeing-hyprland-plugin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, wellbeing-common, dbus, hyprland (>= 0.41)
Description: Hyprland compositor plugin for Digital Wellbeing
 Renders block overlays via OpenGL and emits FocusChanged / ActivityChanged
 signals. Requires Hyprland >= 0.41.
